émon together, it is probably based on a {{wp|coat of arms}}. The fact that it started off as an ordinary sword as a {{p|Honedge}} may mean it could be based on the {{wp|bushido}} mythos behind {{wp|katana}} use; katanas possessed the user {{wp|samurai}}\'s soul and attacked of its own free will. Visually, considering its build and hilt, Doublade seems to be based on a pair of either {{wp|spatha}}, {{wp|claymore}}, or possibly {{wp|jian}} swords with their own {{wp|scabbard}}s, {{wp|Hilt#Sword knot|tassel}}-like prehensile limbs, and a shared shield connecting its scabbards together.\n\n====Name origin====\nDoublade is a combination of \'\'double\'\' and \'\'blade\'\'.\n\nNidangill may be a combination of 二 \'\'ni\'\' (two), 断 \'\'dan\'\' (to sever), and 斬る \'\'kiru\'\' (to slay with a blade) or \'\'kill\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Steel|type2=Ghost\n|ja=ニダンギル \'\'Nidangill\'\'|jameaning=Possibly {{tt|二 \'\'ni\'\'|two}}, {{tt|断 \'\'dan\'\' |to sever}}, and {{tt|斬る \'\'kiru\'\'|to slay with a blade}} or \'\'kill\'\'\n|fr=Dimoclès|frmeaning=From \'\'{{tt|di-|Prefix for &quot;two&quot;}}\'\' and \'\'{{wp|Damocles}}\'\'\n|es=Doublade|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Duokles|demeaning=From \'\'duo\'\' and \'\'{{tt|Damokles|Damocles}}\'\'\n|it=Doublade|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=쌍검킬 \'\'Ssanggeomkil\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|쌍 (雙) \'\'ssang\'\'|pair, twin}}, {{tt|검 (劍) \'\'geom\'\'|sword}}, and \'\'kill\'\'\n|zh_cmn=雙劍鞘 \'\'Shuāngjiànqiào\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|雙 \'\'shuāng\'\'|double}}, {{tt|劍 \'\'jiàn\'\'|sword}}, and {{tt|鞘 \'\'qiào\'\'|sheath}}\n|zh_yue=雙劍鞘 \'\'Sēunggimchiu\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=From {{tt|雙 \'\'sēung\'\'|double}}, {{tt|劍 \'\'gim\'\'|sword}}, and {{tt|鞘 \'\'chiu\'\'|sheath}}\n|hi=डबलेड \'\'Doublade\'\'|himeaning=Transcription of English name\n|ru=Дублейд \'\'Dubleyd\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n{{-}}\n\n==Notes==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Steel|type2=Ghost}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Steel|prevnum=679|prev=Honedge|nextnum=681|next=Aegislash}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[Category:Pokémon that evolve using Dusk Stone]]\n[[Category:Pokémon that evolve by evolutionary stone]]\n\n[[de:Duokles]]\n[[es:Doublade]]\n[[fr:Dimoclès]]\n[[it:Doublade]]\n[[ja:ニダンギル]]\n[[zh:双剑鞘]]'}